pullRequest.body:
and equivalence with the existence of a CompositionSeries.

Add order-theoretic results: a simple order is finite; WellFoundedLT implies every non-top element is covered by some other element, and the dual result; WellFoundedLT + WellFoundedGT implies there exists a finite sequence from ‚ä• to ‚ä§ with each element covering the previous one.

Also generalize two proof_wanted statements about semisimple modules/rings.

---

- [x] depends on: #17425
